HUbV-6li4Vi8itk554CGz9qaGFE", "publicIdentifier": "axeljehangir", "recommendations/0/context": "Axel was Krish's client", "recommendations/0/date": "October 9, 2023", "recommendations/0/description": "Working with Krish was a pleasure. He understood our needs and was able to work autonomously achieving results for us. His understanding of the hotel industry and hotel needs were extremely beneficial for us and his recommendations to fine tune our online activities were rewarding.\nHaving a direct line to him on whatsapp ensured that he and his team were very responsive and always delivered earlier than we anticipated.\nI will not hesitate to work with Krish again in the near future.", "recommendations/0/name": "Krish Purnawarman", "recommendations/0/subtitle": "SEO,IA, Google Analytics-Ads, Bing PPC. Facebook Ads, Instagram Ads eCommerce Digital Marketing Consultant Jakarta, Bali", "recommendations/0/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/krishpurnawarman/", "recommendations/0/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAHAT1IBLQqRmEjpqHEsWwsv8_2P72Nf0fU", "recommendations/1/context": "Axel was senior to Catarina but didn't manage Catarina directly", "recommendations/1/date": "June 6, 2020", "recommendations/1/description": "I've had the pleasure to work with Catarina during the preopening and operating phases of Anantara Quy Nhon Villas. She has demonstrated great leadership reflected in the efficiency of her team and through the satisfaction of our guests. I highly recommend Catarina and would not hesitate to work with her again in the future.", "recommendations/1/name": "Catarina Simões", "recommendations/1/subtitle": "General Manager", "recommendations/1/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/catarina22simoes/", "recommendations/1/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAXEfwoB3PJn3K50Irkr6sme3Wn-lh5dbEY", "recommendations/2/context": "Axel worked with Gabriele on the same team", "recommendations/2/date": "May 24, 2015", "recommendations/2/description": "I have worked alongside Gabriele for almost 3 years - Gabriele is a very reliable member of the team, a great team player, and always with solutions - his relationship with the Sales and Marketing team was key to the success of the S&M department - I would work alongside him again without a doubt. Gabriele is an asset to any property he will be with. ", "recommendations/2/name": "Gabriele Noe", "recommendations/2/subtitle": "Director at Marcopolo Trading Phuket (Made in Thailand food products supplier)", "recommendations/2/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/gabriele-noe-406aa724/", "recommendations/2/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAUlE4YB2_CZqqPERDW0XFgmewxAIvHMxs8", "recommendationsReceived/0/context": "Chris managed Axel directly", "recommendationsReceived/0/date": "March 20, 2017", "recommendationsReceived/0/description": "Axel is a talented individual with a great career ahead of him.\nHis drive and enthusiasm is a pleasure to witness whilst his thirst for ever greater knowledge and experience proves he will always succeed wherever he finds himself.\nAxel is an asset to any organisation in the hospitality sector.\n\n", "recommendationsReceived/0/name": "Chris Bailey", "recommendationsReceived/0/subtitle": "Hotel, hospitality & tourism operating executive delivering growth by connecting commercials, strategy, operations and people skills.", "recommendationsReceived/0/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/chris-bailey-70a72b1/", "recommendationsReceived/0/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAABJFDoB9tgnl6Zu1avL6Zxzz6lfnAVmOok", "recommendationsReceived/1/context": "Marie-Laure managed Axel directly", "recommendationsReceived/1/date": "November 18, 2016", "recommendationsReceived/1/description": "I had the pleasure to work with Axel when he joined us as part of the Boathouse reopening team back in December 2011. Axel was instrumental in the successful rebranding and re-launching of this iconic hotel in the south of Phuket post renovation and  under new ownership and management after 22 years of existence. He brings with him an innovative way of looking at sales, is plentiful of interesting ideas and definitely displays an ‘out of the box’ thinking approach. A very energetic, professional, motivated and positive member of the team with whom I thoroughly enjoyed working.", "recommendationsReceived/1/name": "Marie-Laure Fleury", "recommendationsReceived/1/subtitle": "General Manager at Four Seasons Hotel London at Tower Bridge", "recommendationsReceived/1/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/marie-laure-fleury-b3051411/", "recommendationsReceived/1/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAJjvlQBsEiBjhm5GA4A2DkDHBif9WS7eow", "recommendationsReceived/2/context": "Gabriele worked with Axel on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/2/date": "November 13, 2016", "recommendationsReceived/2/description": "    I worked with Axel for almost 3 years he is certainly is someone who knows the value of relationships in business and appreciates the value of a win - win scenario for both parties. He is well respected and has been a valuable asset to the Hotel ,efficiently managing the S&M department and often in operation with a busy over 550room hotel.\n\nAxel is a great leader with lots of great marketing ideas. He communicates his ideas well and allows us and his other team members to have input with our own impute\n\nHe has always been polite and respectful to everyone, I would easily work with him again at anytime.\n", "recommendationsReceived/2/name": "Gabriele Noe", "recommendationsReceived/2/subtitle": "Director at Marcopolo Trading Phuket (Made in Thailand food products supplier)", "recommendationsReceived/2/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/gabriele-noe-406aa724/", "recommendationsReceived/2/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAUlE4YB2_CZqqPERDW0XFgmewxAIvHMxs8", "recommendationsReceived/3/context": "Leanne managed Axel directly", "recommendationsReceived/3/date": "September 8, 2015", "recommendationsReceived/3/description": "I had the pleasure of working with Axel Jehangir during my time as Sales & Marketing Director at Trisara Phuket. Axel was an absolute delight to work with and led the Sales team for the Boathouse during the initial launch phase of reopening with new management. A highly ambitious member of the team dedicated to creating new sales leads and always focused on closing. ", "recommendationsReceived/3/name": "Leanne Reddie", "recommendationsReceived/3/subtitle": "Chief Commercial Officer I Asset Management I Luxury Hotelier I MBA", "recommendationsReceived/3/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/leannereddie/", "recommendationsReceived/3/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAEWZpUBlF3dU6l6KcGnJ4k4TnmfRsPgWFc", "recommendationsReceived/4/context": "Friedrich managed Axel directly", "recommendationsReceived/4/date": "May 9, 2012", "recommendationsReceived/4/description": "As a Sales executive with the Laguna Holiday Club, Axel reported indirectly to me.\nAxel is a gifted and talented multilingual, sales and marketing executive with great management potential. Any organization is lucky to have him on board. \n\nF.W.M. Zielinski", "recommendationsReceived/4/name": "Friedrich Zielinski", "recommendationsReceived/4/subtitle": "Hospitality industry veteran who likes to think outside of the box", "recommendationsReceived/4/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/friedrich-zielinski-b653193/", "recommendationsReceived/4/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAACUqD0B7K0K8_5rUCOUKG4EOh_e7CHdrGo", "skills/0/title": "Resort Development", "skills/1/title": "Commercial Operation", "skills/2/title": "Concept Development", "skills/3/title": "Financial Analysis", "skills/4/title": "Wellness", "skills/5/title": "Hotel Management", "skills/6/title": "Hotels", "skills/7/title": "Resorts", "skills/8/title": "Hospitality Industry", "skills/9/title": "Hospitality Management", "skills/10/title": "Hospitality", "skills/11/title": "Tourism", "skills/12/title": "Front Office", "skills/13/title": "Pre-opening", "skills/14/title": "Rooms Division", "skills/15/title": "Yield Management", "s