u Kalai M and hope to work with you again in the near future.", "recommendations/0/name": "Kalai. Kay", "recommendations/0/subtitle": "Executive Assistant Manager at Hard Rock International", "recommendations/0/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/kalaivanthanm/", "recommendations/0/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAS1yaABWBn0My0z3bP-b7HuUmIzj5JM9bA", "recommendations/1/context": "Natsurang was senior to Nathathichat but didn't manage Nathathichat directly", "recommendations/1/date": "June 11, 2013", "recommendations/1/description": "Nathaphong he have leadership skill, he can manage the team very well.\nHigh standard of service recovery. He always confident him self to solve the guest problem, and also make god relationship with other department at all the time.", "recommendations/1/name": "Nathathichat Charoenyut", "recommendations/1/subtitle": "Front Office Manager at Trinity Silom Hotel", "recommendations/1/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/nathathichat-charoenyut-a7748348/", "recommendations/1/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAoJUjsB28SelPaIELTDAu47WuDScbymits", "recommendations/2/context": "Natsurang managed Nathathichat directly", "recommendations/2/date": "June 11, 2013", "recommendations/2/description": "Nathaphong he always show out standing performance, willing to learn newly experience, hard working, good relationship with other department, follow the job which is assign by his supervisor with care, consistency and be honest with his job at all the time.", "recommendations/2/name": "Nathathichat Charoenyut", "recommendations/2/subtitle": "Front Office Manager at Trinity Silom Hotel", "recommendations/2/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/nathathichat-charoenyut-a7748348/", "recommendations/2/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAoJUjsB28SelPaIELTDAu47WuDScbymits", "recommendations/3/context": "Natsurang managed Nathathichat directly", "recommendations/3/date": "June 4, 2012", "recommendations/3/description": "Nathaphong is the one of my staff that I recommend to hire as he is very strong people in the front office, active, fast to learn, helpful, friendly, hard worker, good attitude and positive thinking. He always respond his job very well and try to solve the guest's problem, he can handle very well when the guests complains other staff or other department because he have the owner ship skill. Well done Mr.Nathaphong.", "recommendations/3/name": "Nathathichat Charoenyut", "recommendations/3/subtitle": "Front Office Manager at Trinity Silom Hotel", "recommendations/3/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/nathathichat-charoenyut-a7748348/", "recommendations/3/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAoJUjsB28SelPaIELTDAu47WuDScbymits", "recommendationsReceived/0/context": "John managed Natsurang directly", "recommendationsReceived/0/date": "May 28, 2018", "recommendationsReceived/0/description": "Siriwan is an excellent General Manager that understands the importance of balancing the guest experience with the profitability of the hotel.  A natural leader that is respected and one that mentors her management team to achieve at all times.  Siriwan has a natural affinity for her team and inspires loyalty from all.", "recommendationsReceived/0/name": "John Bendtsen", "recommendationsReceived/0/subtitle": "General Manager", "recommendationsReceived/0/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/john-bendtsen-03239a13/", "recommendationsReceived/0/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAK58KYBJztQxJ2kh-TRrRv9qgQe5A2iP2I", "recommendationsReceived/1/context": "Robert managed Natsurang directly", "recommendationsReceived/1/date": "January 30, 2014", "recommendationsReceived/1/description": "Khun Siriwan is an amazing manager who can lead a large team very effectively and caringly. Her unique ability lies in diffusing situations before they become major issues. Whether with Guests, Subordinates or superiors her communication is respectful and respectable. The is a true leader who has a very good understanding of the hospitality business and has numerous commercially successful ideas to recommend. It was a delight to have her.", "recommendationsReceived/1/name": "Robert Mayer MBA", "recommendationsReceived/1/subtitle": "Developing Residential and Hospitality Real Estate", "recommendationsReceived/1/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/robertkmayer/", "recommendationsReceived/1/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAJT0MUBqHizDgEf1HNbgm8-mpaAmMewaHM", "recommendationsReceived/2/context": "Ramil worked with Natsurang on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/2/date": "January 29, 2014", "recommendationsReceived/2/description": "Siriwan as a manager is a very efficient one. She consistently achieved her goal with a minimum use of resources. She also always meet her KPI's target. As a leader, her associates look at her with respect and as a role model. She meets her deadlines on time. Have a sense of ownership, initiative and teamwork. She also shows the passion and pride for what she is doing.", "recommendationsReceived/2/name": "Ramil Lagos", "recommendationsReceived/2/subtitle": "Executive Housekeeper", "recommendationsReceived/2/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/ramil-lagos-621a1129/", "recommendationsReceived/2/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAYF4zkB4RzJ29HBrq_v2lBGzL4BHTb37u0", "recommendationsReceived/3/context": "Kalai. worked with Natsurang on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/3/date": "June 30, 2012", "recommendationsReceived/3/description": "Ms. Siriwan is a self starter always comes up with great ideas while facing any difficulties or challenges during operations. She works well not only with all level of her associates importantly with all other department personal involved in day to day operation. She is a true professional and a great leader. \n\nMs. Siriwan is very clear minded and positive person who is able to simplify complicated situations and solve them effectively. She is a leader who allows her people to assume responsibility for their operations and actions. \n\nShe always had innovative & creative idea to keep improving the quality of guests experience and a leader who can trust that she will drive you to be successfully in your career.  Ms. Siriwan is a hardworking individual who takes prides in her job and executes them with diligence.\n\nI have greatly enjoyed working with Ms. Siriwan. It was a privilege to work with her at Centara Grand Maldives. All the best to Ms.Siriwan  and I`m sure she will be General Manager sooner as she have all the capabilities and talent in hospitality business, I hope to work with her again and be a part of her working subordinate in near future.", "recommendationsReceived/3/name": "Kalai. Kay", "recommendationsReceived/3/subtitle": "Executive Assistant Manager at Hard Rock International", "recommendationsReceived/3/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/kalaivanthanm/", "recommendationsReceived/3/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAS1yaABWBn0My0z3bP-b7HuUmIzj5JM9bA", "recommendationsReceived/4/context": "Nathathichat worked with Natsurang but they were at different companies", "recommendationsReceived/4/date": "June 5, 2012", "recommendationsReceived/4/description": "“Khun Siriwan is an excellent person to work with. She is focused, sincere & dedicated towards her work. She has excellent team spirit – she is one who will be there to guide, support, teach and help; anyone and everyone. She is a thorough professional and it has been a pleasure working with her.”", "recommendationsReceived/4/name": "Nathathichat Charoenyut", "recommendationsReceived/4/subtitle": "Front Office Manager at Trinity Silom Hotel", "recommendationsReceived/4/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/nathathichat-charoenyut-a7748348/", "recommendationsReceived/4/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAoJUjsB28SelPaIELTDAu47WuDScbymits", "skills/0/title": "Recruiting", "skills/1/title": "Nonprofit Organizations", "skills/2/title": "Human Resources (HR)", "skills/3/title": "General Management", "skills/4/title": "Team Leadership", "skills/5/title": "Rooms Division", "skills/6/title": "Op